Definition: a disorder of eating in which the person alternates between strong craving for food and aversion to food
Example: characterized by excessive eating followed by periods of fasting or self-induced vomiting
Synonyms: binge-purge_syndrome, binge-vomit_syndrome, bulima_nervosa, eating_disorder, a, disorder, of, eating, in, which, the, person, alternates, between, strong, craving, for, food, and, aversion, to, characterized, by, excessive, followed, periods, fasting, or, self-induced, vomiting
Category: noun.state
